    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "description": {
      "content": "The Binance Copy Trading API allows developers to interact with the copy trading platform where users can automatically replicate the trades of experienced lead traders. The API provides endpoints for managing copy trading positions, querying lead trader portfolios and performance metrics, and configuring copy trading parameters.\n\nContact Support:\n Name: Binance Support",
